#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>You didn't import demo data?</strong> You can still do it. Go to "
"Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Hardware Shop package and check the "
"related box."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Etkö tuonut demotietoja?</strong> Voit yhä tehdä sen. Siirry kohtaan "
"Sovellukset &gt; Toimialat &gt; Päivitä laitteistomyymäläsi ja ruksaa "
"olennainen laatikko."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Website</span></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders directly "
"in Odoo and go live with your <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">E-"
"shop</span></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"Ilmainen, personoitu, integroitu <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Verkkosivu</span></strong> vain muutamalla klikkauksella. Ota tilauksia "
"vastaan suoraan Odoossa ja julkaise oma <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Verkkokauppa</span></strong> vain minuuteissa."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Ace Hardware is already registered in your database; select it using the "
"\"Customer\" button."
msgstr ""
"Ace Hardware on jo rekisteröity tietokantaasi; valitse se painamalla "
"\"Asiakas\"-painiketta."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add your customer, and the product they want."
msgstr "Lisää asiakkaasi ja tuote, jonka hän haluaa."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any specific manufacture process in your shop? (Cutting wood panels, "
"assemblies...). Try the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Manufacture "
"App</span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"Onko sinulla joitakin tiettyjä tuotantoprosesseja kaupassasi (puulevyjen "
"leikkaus, kokoaminen,...)? Kokeile <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;"
"\">Tuotanto-sovellusta</span></strong>"

